            <br>

            <p class="Info"> The content must be readable and understandable. </p>

            <br>

            <h2>3.1.1 Language of the page</h2>
            <p class="Info">The default human language of each web page can be programmatically determined.</p>
            <p class="Info"> The HTML code must contain a valid language code.</p>
            <p class="Info"> The language set in the code must be the same language as the content of the web page. </p>

            <br>

